name: International Conference on Vision Computing
content: International Conference on Vision Computing (VISCOM 2023) will provide an excellent internationalforum for sharing knowledge and results in theory, methodology and applications of Vision Computing. Authors are solicited to contribute to this Conference by submitting articles that illustrate research results, projects, surveying works and industrial experiences that describe significant advances in the Vision Computing.
